data.description: Investment opportunity if you are looking to maintain an all brick two unit building.  Neat and clean 2 unit offers the option to convert back to a single family house as well. Covered front porch, short distance to busline and highway into town, spacious second floor 3 BR unit.  Plaster walls, roof 2009, windows-2009 and some areas throughout recently painted. Two equipped kitchens, good closet areas and large shared basement.  Some original woodwork and fireplaces.
